      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ファッションショー当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On the day of the fashion show",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ついにこの日が来たな\n血の滲むような特訓の成果を見せる時が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally‚ the day has come.\nThe time to show the results of our training…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……えっと、天動さん？\nどうして不満顔なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ Tendo-san.\nWhat's bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "今日の私の衣装、普段使い出来る\nカジュアルなファッションなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The outfit I'm wearing today is something I can wear casually.\nIt's just a casual fashion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ドレスとピンヒールだと勝手に思い込んでいたので\n拍子抜けしたと言うか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had assumed it would be a dress and high heels‚\nSo I'm kind of disappointed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく10cmのピンヒールで歩く練習をしたのに\n結局必要なくて……私の苦労はなんだったのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I went through the trouble of practicing walking in 10cm high heels‚\nonly to find out they weren't necessary… What was the point of my efforts…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "カジュアルなのは予想外だったが、いい服じゃないか\nとても爽やかで似合っている。凄く綺麗だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was unexpected that it's a casual outfit‚ but it looks good.\nIt's very refreshing and suits you. You look really beautiful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "き、綺麗……あ、ありがとうございます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-Beautiful… Ah‚ thank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、天動さんがしてきた努力は無駄じゃない\nモデルとしての技術や心構えは確実に身についている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ the efforts Tendo-san've put in aren't in vain.\nYou have definitely acquired modeling skills and the right mindset.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね\nどんな服だろうと私のやることは変わりません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right.\nNo matter what clothes I wear‚ my job remains the same.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "この服にはデザイナーの想いが込められています\nその想いを観客に伝えるのがモデルの仕事……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These clothes carry the designer's intentions.\nIt's the model's job to convey those intentions to the audience…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "この服がショーの主役になるように\nランウェイで最高のパフォーマンスをするだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just have to give the best performance on the runway\nSo that this outfit becomes the star of the show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n私の一世一代のウォーキングを見ていて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nPlease watch my once-in-a-lifetime walk!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ファッションショー終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――ファッションショー終了後",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\n私のウォーキングはどうでしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your hard work‚ {user}-san.\nHow was my walk?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "プロのモデルかと思うくらい\n様になってて、凄く良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was so professional that I thought you were a pro model.\nYou looked amazing‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんもとても盛り上がっていて\n今日のファッションショーは大成功だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and the audience was really excited.\nToday's fashion show was a big success.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。実は会場で\n合同練習の時に一緒だったモデルと会ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Actually‚ I met a model at the venue\nWho was also in the joint practice with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "彼女は私のウォーキングを見て\n見違えるほどうまくなったって驚いていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was surprised at\nhow much I had improved in my walk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "「貴方がどれだけ真剣に取り組んだか一目で分かった\nアイドルだからってバカにしてごめんなさい」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said‚ \"I could tell at a glance how seriously you worked on it.\nI'm sorry for underestimating you just because you're an idol\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "素直に謝られてしまいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She apologized sincerely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんの頑張りが認められたんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san's hard work was recognized.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "はい、努力した甲斐がありました\nファッションショーも無事に終わってホッとしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ my efforts paid off.\nI'm relieved that the fashion show ended successfully.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "これで{user}さんと居残り練習する\nこともなくなると思うと少し寂しい気もしますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although I feel a little lonely knowing that\nThere won't be any more extra practice with you‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "気を抜くのはまだ早いぞ\nこの後、会場の外で撮影があるんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's too early to let your guard down.\nDon't you have a photoshoot outside the venue later?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "今日の衣装で撮影の予定です\nでも撮影開始までまだ時間がありますから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have a scheduled photoshoot with today's outfit.\nBut we still have some time before the shoot starts…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
